Package: textab
Title: Create Highly-Customized LaTeX Tables in R
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
      person("Thibaut", "Lamadon", , "thibaut.lamadon@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cph")),
      person("Bradley", "Setzler", , "bradley.setzler@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre","cph"))
    )
Description: This package generates LaTeX tables directly from R. It builds LaTeX tables in blocks, in the spirit of ggplot2, using the + and - operators for concatenation in the vertical or horizontal direction, respectively. It exports tables in the LaTeX tabular environment in .tex code. It can compiled a .pdf document from the .tex code.
